    "body": "### Description\n\nI am currently trying to setup intelephense to work and need to increase the max file size (\"intelephense.files.maxSize\" = 1500000).\r\nI see in the docs that we should be able to set this as follows \r\n```\r\nlspconfig.intelephense.setup({\r\n\tcapabilities = capabilities,\r\n\tsettings = {\r\n\t\tintelephense = {\r\n\t\t\tfiles = {\r\n\t\t\t\tmaxSize = 1500000,\r\n\t\t\t},\r\n\t\t},\r\n\t},\r\n})\r\n```\r\nUpon using the following:\r\n```\r\n:lua=require('lspconfig').intelephense\r\n```\r\nI do get a block that includes it, but it's listed below the root_dir.\r\nI cannot tell if this is a problem with lspconfig, nvim.lsp, or intelephense.",
